    - target: {fileID: 7827401455826391702, guid: 42f5fe34613bd4f43bcd8761176ac1f0, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Each player has its own corruption bar, which represents instability
        caused by the usage of dark forces. When corruption bar is completely filled,
        the player dies and loses the game.


        Corruption increases when:

        -
        Receiving offensive spells

        - Casting certain high-cost spells

        -
        Making mistakes during the ritual'
