    - target: {fileID: 3469277201729784164, guid: 42f5fe34613bd4f43bcd8761176ac1f0, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Before each match, players build a deck of 6 spells drawn from two
        pools: base cards available to every cult, and exclusive cards unique to
        the cult they belong to.


        During a match, only 3 of those 6 spells
        are available at any given time. Once a spell is cast, it rotates out and
        is replaced by one of the spells from the remaining three.


        Winning
        matches under a cult''s banner allows reaching higher ranks within it, unlocking
        new and more powerful spells.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
